su_wysiwyg_text.value:
This is your Events Page. Here you can list events that pertain to your organization.

To edit the page and remove this placeholder content, click on the "Edit" tab near the top of the page. When finished, be sure to scroll down to the bottom of the page and click "Save."

By default, this page displays "static" content; that is, content that you create, edit, and maintain yourself for this page only.   Your website can also be set up to pull relevant event information directly from Stanford Events (http://events.stanford.edu), thus keeping this page up-to-date automatically. To enable this more advanced functionality, please contact Stanford Web Services, consult our documentation at learnsites.stanford.edu, or pursue any of Stanford's many Drupal self-help and training opportunities.
